{"schemaVersion":1,"bookId":"situational-15000","unitId":"scene-281","title":"色彩缤纷","sectionId":"chapter-12","sectionTitle":"休闲娱乐无极限","pageStart":1369,"pageEnd":1373,"extractionMethod":"text-layer","wordEntryCount":33,"duplicateEntryCount":9,"pages":[{"number":1369,"blocks":[{"type":"title","text":"281 色彩缤纷"},{"type":"section","text":"Step1 场景词"},{"type":"entry","text":"colourful [ˈkʌləfl]","headword":"colourful"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.五彩缤纷的"},{"type":"note","text":"◎colourful life多彩人生"},{"type":"entry","text":"colourful days五彩缤纷的日子","headword":"colourful days"},{"type":"entry","text":"primary colour 原色","headword":"primary colour"},{"type":"entry","text":"red [red]","headword":"red"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.红色"},{"type":"entry","text":"green [ɡriːn]","headword":"green"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.绿色"},{"type":"entry","text":"army green军绿色","headword":"army green"},{"type":"entry","text":"blue [bluː]","headword":"blue"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.蓝色"},{"type":"note","text":"◎navy blue海军蓝色"}]},{"number":1370,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"midnight blue深蓝色","headword":"midnight blue"},{"type":"entry","text":"additive colour 加色","headword":"additive colour"},{"type":"entry","text":"yellow [ˈjeləʊ]","headword":"yellow"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.黄色"},{"type":"entry","text":"indigo [ˈɪndɪɡəʊ]","headword":"indigo"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.靛蓝色"},{"type":"entry","text":"purple [ˈpɜːpl]","headword":"purple"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.紫色"},{"type":"note","text":"◎dark purple深紫色，暗紫色"},{"type":"entry","text":"black [blæk]","headword":"black"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.黑色"},{"type":"entry","text":"white [waɪt]","headword":"white"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.白色"},{"type":"entry","text":"pink [pɪŋk]","headword":"pink"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.粉色"},{"type":"entry","text":"grey [ɡreɪ]","headword":"grey"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.灰色"},{"type":"entry","text":"colour mixture 混色","headword":"colour mixture"},{"type":"entry","text":"carmine [ˈkɑːmaɪn]","headword":"carmine"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.胭脂红色，深红色"}]},{"number":1371,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"auburn [ˈɔːbən]","headword":"auburn"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./a.红褐色（的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"ivory [ˈaɪvəri]","headword":"ivory"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.乳白色，象牙色"},{"type":"note","text":"◎ivory white象牙白色"},{"type":"entry","text":"beige [beɪʒ]","headword":"beige"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./a.米黄色（的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"light [laɪt]","headword":"light"},{"type":"definition","text":"a.浅色的"},{"type":"entry","text":"theory of colour 色彩理论","headword":"theory of colour"}]},{"number":1372,"blocks":[{"type":"entry","text":"warm tone 暖色调","headword":"warm tone"},{"type":"entry","text":"cold tone 冷色调","headword":"cold tone"},{"type":"entry","text":"colourisation [ˌkʌləraɪˈzeɪʃn]","headword":"colourisation"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.着色"},{"type":"entry","text":"complementary colour 互补色","headword":"complementary colour"},{"type":"entry","text":"colour wheel 色轮","headword":"colour wheel"},{"type":"entry","text":"colour temperature 色温","headword":"colour temperature"},{"type":"entry","text":"monochrome [ˈmɒnəkrəʊm]","headword":"monochrome"},{"type":"definition","text":"n./a.黑白（的）；单色（的）"},{"type":"entry","text":"monochrome image单色图像","headword":"monochrome image"},{"type":"entry","text":"greyscale [ˈɡreɪskeɪl]","headword":"greyscale"},{"type":"definition","text":"n.灰度"},{"type":"section","text":"Step2 学以致用"},{"type":"text","text":"有趣的小词blue"},{"type":"text","text":"很多电影名字跟blue有关，比如The Big Blue（《碧海蓝天》）以"},{"type":"text","text":"及Into the Blue（《碧海追踪》），这两部影片故事的背景都离不开大"},{"type":"text","text":"海。还有一部警匪片Dark Blue（《深蓝》），通过描述一个小人物身"}]},{"number":1373,"blocks":[{"type":"text","text":"边的故事来表现一些让人不得不思考的“大问题”，这个blue就取了"},{"type":"text","text":"其“忧郁”的含义。"},{"type":"text","text":"1. I really have the blues today. 我今天情绪很不好。"},{"type":"text","text":"这里的blue是指“忧郁的情绪”。据说，世上有些blue devils（蓝魔"},{"type":"text","text":"鬼）是会使人忧郁的，所以He is seized/afflicted with the blue devils."},{"type":"text","text":"即“他闷闷不乐”。"},{"type":"text","text":"2. She arrived out of the blue. 她没有事先告知就来了。"},{"type":"entry","text":"Out of the blue的意思是“意外的，未事先告知的”，相当于","headword":"Out of the blue"}]}]}